other_tests.findings: No histopathological abnormalities (no lymphoid infiltrates, deposits, necrosis, granulomas, or multinucleated giant cells; stains for C3b and C4b negative).
Ruled out obstructive coronary artery disease.
Revealed a compound heterozygous pathogenic variant in RNU4ATAC [NR_023343.1:n.118T>C, autosomal recessive (AR) inheritance, heterozygous; mother is heterozygous and father is negative, pathogenic].
